37
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,000
Could I talk to you in private?

38
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,200
Just stand there and speak.

39
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,440
But how could she...

40
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,200
Then...

41
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,280
I also saw that man.

42
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,000
Now

43
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,959
