47
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,680
No, my tongue is so cute.

48
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,440
Scared?

49
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,080
No.

50
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:10,200
I really know that man.

51
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,440
Speak.

52
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,720
What can I get in return

53
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,600
