54
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,720
What do you want?

55
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,400
I want...

56
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,840
I want you not to move.

57
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,560
Mister Li,

58
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,840
I'm not sure

59
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,760
if I shall tell you this.

60
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,760
I have been grateful to you.

61
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,480
Maybe you forgot it already,

62
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,680
but I could never

63
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:42,519
forget that day.

64
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,680
It

65
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,559
was such a cold day

66
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,880
and your body

67
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:54,480
was so warm.

68
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,600
Give it to me.

69
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:06,880
What?

70
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,960
The thing in your hand.

71
