75
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,400
Who sent me?

76
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,000
I just cut your hair

77
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,680
to return your favor.

78
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,720
It's said

79
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:37,159
that if one's hair is buried at Town God Temple,

80
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,120
its owner may be prayed

81
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
for to always be safe.

82
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,760
Do you have to wear those to return the favor?

83
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,240
I thought men all liked it.

84
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,240
Childish.

85
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,920
Don't think

86
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,040
about useless things.

87
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,560
I'm warning you

88
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,680
that if you dare

89
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,359
to lie to me about Ji Bofeng,

90
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,200
I will kill you.

91
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,280
I'm sorry

92
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,680
because I didn't see him.

93
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:12,560
But if I see him later,

94
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,760
will you see me again?

95
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:17,120
When you find him.

96
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,560
Qingshui Street.

97
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,560
The south of Yong'an Town.

98
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,840
Qiyue Calligraphy.

99
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,680
Wait. Why can't I find it?

100
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,920
Come out.

101
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,080
Why did you leave me alone again yesterday?

102
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,400
Because I met someone I knew.

103
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,440
An old friend.

104
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,200
An old friend?

105
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,000
By the way,

106
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,520
how could she see you?

107
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,640
She has Yin-Yang Eyes.

108
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,680
We knew each other long ago.

109
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,080
But we haven't contacted each other

110
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,520
since I went to war.

111
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,200
I see.

112
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,200
No wonder she seemed to be looking at a ghost.

113
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,400
Heroine,

114
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,560
what are you looking for?

115
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,920
Li Bugui is looking for someone

116
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,359
named Ji Bofeng.

117
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:52,040
I have got Li Bugui's hair.

118
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:54,360
If I find this Ji Bofeng,

119
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,440
I can get close to Li Bugui again.

120
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:57,359
Then

121
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,040
I will get his tears

122
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,920
or blood.

123
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,000
Shumiao Pavilion

124
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,440
has the records of all the natives,

125
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,200
but

126
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,160
I have never heard

127
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:09,400
about Ji Bofeng.

128
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,440
Anyway, don't worry.

129
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,040
Shumiao Pavilion

130
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,200
is a base for all Town Gods.

131
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,479
So there is everything

132
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:23,640
about the people from the nobles

133
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,000
to the newborn babies.

134
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,200
Let me write a letter

135
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,960
to tell all the Town Gods in Qingchuan to look for him.

136
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,480
Really?

137
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,200
Yes.

138
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,440
Thank you, Xie.

139
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,360
No problem.

140
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,760
It's just

141
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,159
I have a question.

142
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,880
What is it?

143
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,200
Heroine, how did you

144
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,680
get a physical body in Qingchuan?

145
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,040
The Camouflage Beast?

146
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,440
Yes.

147
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,080
It's granted by His Majesty,

148
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:07,000
it offers me a physical figure here.

149
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,480
But one of its petals

150
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,160
drops each seven days.

151
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,719
If I can't go back

152
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,080
in 49 days,

153
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,920
I will feel extremely itchy and sore

154
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,160
and suffer the biting of worms

155
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,040
till I'm totally engulfed.

156
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,200
Then I can

157
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,599
never go back.

158
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,680
Trust me.

159
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,760
I will help you to complete the mission

160
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,960
before the petals disappear.

161
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,680
I'm sending the message right now.

162
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:52,040
A letter from the Town God of Huangling.

163
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,800
I have checked the records of three centuries

164
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,480
and only found one person who was like Ji Bofeng,

165
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,000
but that man died

166
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,120
210 years ago.

167
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,600
Died?

168
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:05,319
Yes.

169
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,920
A letter

170
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,240
From the Town God of Youyun.

171
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,120
