173
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,200
From Taohua Town.

174
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,000
Yunmeng Town.

175
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,960
Jiuzhou Town.

176
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,880
Xilan Town.

177
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,480
Yong'an Town.

178
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,160
Tianshui Town.

179
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,560
A letter...

180
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:22,079
A letter from

181
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,840
From the Town God of Luohua.

182
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,120
So, heroine,

183
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,960
impressed

184
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,920
by my connections?

185
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,360
Yes.

186
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,360
Let's go back to check them.

187
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:31,800
Okay.

188
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,200
It's weird.

189
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,040
