191
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,640
This man is still alive.

192
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,439
He should be in Luohua.

193
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,000
Tell Li Bugui right now.

194
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,199
No.

195
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:17,000
I lied to him once,

196
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,640
