198
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,920
I'll go to Luohua Town

199
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:26,400
to invite Ji Bofeng back.

200
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,160
Li Bugui will be grateful to me

201
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,000
for seeing his savior.

202
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,240
Hold on.

203
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,120
I can't leave my own town.

204
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,360
